<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 00:34:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>回顾普珥节的故事，数千人在特拉维夫集会要求释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/recalling-the-story-of-purim-thousands-rally-in-tel-aviv-for-the-release-of-the-hostages/0000018e-6ca0-d8e8-a9de-7cbbe4b10000</link><description>“这样的事情是不可接受的，在我们的犹太教中是不可接受的”：在讲述哈曼试图消灭犹太人的普珥节故事时，仍被扣押在加沙的人质家属恳求全国团结起来，将他们全部带回家</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 21:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/recalling-the-story-of-purim-thousands-rally-in-tel-aviv-for-the-release-of-the-hostages/0000018e-6ca0-d8e8-a9de-7cbbe4b10000</guid></item><item><title>“自加沙战争以来，我更加认识到抵制以色列是必要的。但我做不到&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-gaza-war-i-moved-closer-to-the-idea-of-boycotting-israel-but-i-cant-do-it/0000018e-6a82-dfa8-a98e-6f8b31590000</link><description>剧作家托尼·库什纳告诉《国土报》播客，他支持乔纳森·格雷泽在加沙演讲中的每一个字，解释了为什么犹太复国主义不等于种族主义，并坚称“左派中有一部分人很天真，比反犹太主义还要天真”。阅读完整采访</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 20:28:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-gaza-war-i-moved-closer-to-the-idea-of-boycotting-israel-but-i-cant-do-it/0000018e-6a82-dfa8-a98e-6f8b31590000</guid></item><item><title>“总理，你很困惑：公众希望所有人质回家”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/prime-minister-you-are-confused-the-public-wants-all-the-hostages-home/0000018e-6caf-d16d-a58e-7cafe5a80000</link><description>以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府和人质协议。在特拉维夫，数百名抗议者纵火并封锁主要道路。仍被扣押在加沙的一名人质的母亲在多哈向以色列代表团发表讲话：“你们正在履行自己一生的使命——没有人质协议就不要回来”</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 20:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/prime-minister-you-are-confused-the-public-wants-all-the-hostages-home/0000018e-6caf-d16d-a58e-7cafe5a80000</guid></item><item><title>官员称以色列同意美国人质交易提议，哈马斯尚未回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-u-s-hostage-deal-proposal-hamas-yet-to-respond-official-says/0000018e-6cb4-d16d-a58e-7cb5daab0000</link><description>据该官员称，该提案涉及释放协议中的首批 40 名人质。哈马斯领导层的消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列官员的言论是“以色列的操纵行为，为继续战争辩护”</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 19:40:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-u-s-hostage-deal-proposal-hamas-yet-to-respond-official-says/0000018e-6cb4-d16d-a58e-7cb5daab0000</guid></item><item><title>你需要知道的，第 169 天：联合国秘书长视察拉法过境点，美国正式禁止向近东救济工程处提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-169-un-chief-visits-rafah-crossing-u-s-blocks-unrwa-funding/0000018e-6c61-d477-abbf-ef617edb0000</link><description>联合国秘书长视察拉法过境点，谴责封锁那里的援助卡车是“道德义愤” ■ 美国正式禁止向近东救济工程处提供资金直至 2025 年 3 月 ■ 以色列国防军表示，在 Al-Shifa 医院拘留了至少 800 名嫌疑人，并杀死了 170 名哈马斯成员 ■ 白宫分享拉法向以色列官员发起进攻的其他选择 ■ 战争结束 169 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 18:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-169-un-chief-visits-rafah-crossing-u-s-blocks-unrwa-funding/0000018e-6c61-d477-abbf-ef617edb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在周五约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-fridays-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-6c60-d1c9-af8f-6ee9ad390000</link><description>中士。伊莱·大卫·加芬克尔 (Ilay David Garfinkel) 中士在以色列国防军杜夫德万部队服役，在士兵们在茂密植被的地区追击时被袭击者杀害。另外七名士兵在袭击中受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 18:18:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-fridays-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-6c60-d1c9-af8f-6ee9ad390000</guid></item><item><title>犹太节日万圣节普珥节简史</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/the-odd-history-of-purim-the-halloween-of-jewish-holidays/00000180-5bae-df19-a7f3-dbfe31760000</link><description>它的起源是什么？什么时候开始的？为什么许多犹太人蔑视普珥节——背后的爱情、谋杀和背叛故事是真的吗？</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 17:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/the-odd-history-of-purim-the-halloween-of-jewish-holidays/00000180-5bae-df19-a7f3-dbfe31760000</guid></item><item><title>民主党警告拜登：以色列作为军事援助接受国不遵守美国法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/democrats-warn-biden-israel-not-in-compliance-with-u-s-law-as-recipients-of-military-aid/0000018e-6bcb-d8e8-a9de-7ffbe23f0000</link><description>民主党议员警告美国总统，内塔尼亚胡政府对向加沙运送人道主义援助的限制使以色列“没有资格继续获得美国武器”，必须纠正这种情况，以免开创“不可接受的先例”</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 16:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/democrats-warn-biden-israel-not-in-compliance-with-u-s-law-as-recipients-of-military-aid/0000018e-6bcb-d8e8-a9de-7ffbe23f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军调查了加沙地带手无寸铁的巴勒斯坦人被空袭身亡的镜头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/idf-probes-footage-of-unarmed-palestinians-struck-from-the-air-killed-in-gaza/0000018e-6a00-dfa8-a98e-6f098aa00000</link><description>半岛电视台发布的一段视频中可以看到四名手无寸铁的人，当时他们正沿着土路行走，然后被空中击中。以色列国防军声称，事件发生在“汗尤尼斯地区的一个活跃战区，该地区的所有平民均已彻底撤离”</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 09:07:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/idf-probes-footage-of-unarmed-palestinians-struck-from-the-air-killed-in-gaza/0000018e-6a00-dfa8-a98e-6f098aa00000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸定居者犹太领袖涉嫌计划破坏巴勒斯坦人的财产</