"true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-22/ty-article/.premium/shelled-and-abandoned-the-galilee-is-another-front-in-israels-multi-arena-war/0000018e-62a2-d507-a1cf-62f611ab0000</guid></item><item><title>全世界都对内塔尼亚胡的计划感到担忧，但没有抓住要点：拉法只是他竞选活动的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-22/ty-article/.premium/the-world-frets-over-netanyahus-plans-but-misses-the-point-rafah-is-part-of-his-campaign/0000018e-62a2-d541-a78e-ffeb99370000</link><description>以色列总理内部不知疲倦的推销员认识到拉法可以作为一个戏剧性的主题，甚至把他的风格带到了总参谋部 ■ 就内塔尼亚胡而言，紧急联合政府已经属于历史的一页</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-22/ty-article/.premium/the-world-frets-over-netanyahus-plans-but-misses-the-point-rafah-is-part-of-his-campaign/0000018e-62a2-d541-a78e-ffeb99370000</guid></item></channel></rss>